            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "The twigjack bramble launches a volley of splinters and brambles in a 10-foot burst within 30 feet that deals 4d6 piercing damage (DC 21 basic Reflex save). When the bramble is reduced to 8 or fewer squares, this area decreases to a 5-foot burst.",
